<paragraph id="FD5A3695FFE6FFA7FF5EFB55FF59FB71" blockId="2.[144,243,1253,1277]" box="[144,243,1253,1277]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">
<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FF5EFB55FF59FB71" box="[144,243,1253,1277]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">Remarks</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FD5A3695FFE6FFA7FF5EFABDFE57F9A9" blockId="2.[144,1104,1293,1701]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">
It has been reported that some species of 
<taxonomicName id="3AE54D16FFE6FFA7FD4BFABDFD5DFAA9" authorityName="Melin" authorityYear="1939" box="[645,759,1293,1317]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FD4BFABDFD5DFAA9" box="[645,759,1293,1317]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">Pagurixus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
have a collar-like protrusion located on the posteromesial portion of the right coxa of the fifth pereopod in males (Komai and 
<bibRefCitation id="99744B64FFE6FFA7FEE2FAFDFE62FAE9" author="Myorin E" box="[300,456,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="1 - 12" refId="ref33305" refString="Komai T and Myorin E. 2005. A new species of Pagurixus (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from southern Japan. Zootaxa 876: 1 - 12." type="journal article" year="2005">Myorin 2005</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="99744B64FFE6FFA7FE14FAFDFCA8FAE9" author="Komai T" box="[474,770,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="507 - 516" refId="ref33173" refString="Komai T. 2006. A new species of Pagurixus Melin, 1939 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan. Zoosystema 28: 507 - 516." type="journal article" year="2006">Komai and Osawa 2006</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="99744B64FFE6FFA7FCD4FAFDFBE5FAE9" author="Komai T" box="[794,1103,1357,1381]" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="507 - 516" refId="ref33173" refString="Komai T. 2006. A new species of Pagurixus Melin, 1939 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan. Zoosystema 28: 507 - 516." type="journal article" year="2006">Komai and Osawa (2006)</bibRefCitation>
termed this structure “posteromesial protrusion”. The presence of this protrusion is now confirmed in the following nine species (although the developmental degree of it is rather variable according to species): 
<taxonomicName id="3AE54D16FFE6FFA7FDA9FA1DFD51FA49" baseAuthorityName="Melin" baseAuthorityYear="1939" box="[615,763,1453,1477]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="boninensis">
<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FDA9FA1DFD51FA49" box="[615,763,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">P. boninensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="3AE54D16FFE6FFA7FCC0FA1DFC25FA49" authorityName="Komai and Osawa" authorityYear="2006" box="[782,911,1453,1477]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="concolor">
<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FCC0FA1DFC25FA49" box="[782,911,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">P. concolor</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="3AE54D16FFE6FFA7FC6CFA1DFB8EFA49" authority="Komai, 2010" authorityName="Komai" authorityYear="2010" box="[930,1060,1453,1477]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crosnieri" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FC6CFA1DFB8EFA49" box="[930,1060,1453,1477]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">P. crosnieri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="D4A257FCFFE6FFA7FBE1FA1DFF6EFA68" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
; 
<taxonomicName id="3AE54D16FFE6FFA7FF1AFA7DFEF2FA69" authorityName="Komai and Myorin" authorityYear="2005" box="[212,344,1485,1509]" class="Malacostraca" family="Paguridae" genus="Pagurixus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fasciatus">
