<emphasis id="CF91EA87FFE6FFA7FC85FA7DFC6AFA69" box="[843,960,1485,1509]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270">P. paulayi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="99744B64FFE6FFA7FC05FA7DFE88F989" author="Komai T" pageId="2" pageNumber="1270" pagination="507 - 516" refId="ref33173" refString="Komai T. 2006. A new species of Pagurixus Melin, 1939 (Crustacea: Decapoda: Anomura: Paguridae) from the Ryukyu Islands, Japan. Zoosystema 28: 507 - 516." type="journal article" year="2006">Komai and Osawa, 2006</bibRefCitation>
